Rating: 4
delicious soup! it lends itself well to whatever veggies you have on hand. i added green beans and carrots and a little broccoli and just used the one pepper i had. it was a big hit and i will make it again. with my additions, it certainly made more than 4-5 servings.

Rating: 4
This recipe was easy very good. Unlike other reviews, I did not find this to be bland at all. It says 'salt, to taste,' and I think a lot of people tend to under-salt. Anyway, make sure to use enough salt and pepper, and I also used an immersion blender - add the corn (step 3), let it simmer 8 minutes, use an immersion blender. Then add the bell peppers and half-and-half and simmer another 8 minutes uncovered. That will help thicken it and gives it more body. Would definitely make this again!

