Rating: 1
Super bland to me. I doubled the recipe. I used 8c (per suggestions to knock back liquid amount) Heres what I did to make it pretty good after an hour: added a little thyme, a little oregano, celery, 2 tbsps turbinado sugar, 2 cloves garlic, 1/4 c chopped cilantro, tsp cumin. I also think there's just way too many potatoes. I knocked back the onion to 1 1/2. Then I used and imersion (sp?) blender and thickened it with that.

