Rating: 3
This was a great recipe! The suggestion to use 3 cups of broth instead of 5 was right on. We used 1 cup of 1% milk instead of the half and half. We added chopped celery when we put in the corn and peppers, but we should have put it in with the potatoes as it was still a little crunchy. We pureed most of it and added a little cornstarch to thicken it up further. All in all, we would definitely make this soup again.

Rating: 4
